text: Ai Sugiyama and Elena Tatarkova were the defending champions, but did not compete this year. Qualifiers Akiko Morigami and Saori Obata won the title by defeating Alina Jidkova and Bryanne Stewart 6–1, 6–1 in the final. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ===Draw=== ==References== * Main and Qualifying Draws Category:2003 Kroger St. Jude International Category:2003 WTA Tour
